      { icon: "wave", title: "The loop", body: "The worry that speeds up, the checking, the bracing for something that may never come. Familiar, and exhausting." },
      { icon: "compass", title: "What's underneath", body: "A nervous system trying to keep you safe, reading ordinary moments as threats. That's not a flaw. That's just how it works." },
      { icon: "sun", title: "Where it shifts", body: "We work with the system, not against it, so the alarm quiets and you get more room to choose your response." }
    ]
  }) }}
</div>

